---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Community Outreach | SBHS Robotics 750">
     <div class="container">
        <header class="page-header">
            <h1 class="text-glow-gold">Community Outreach</h1>
        </header>
         <div class="about-grid">
            <img src="/girlpowered.png" alt="Team at a community event" style="border-radius: 0.5rem;"/>
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-gradient-gold">Girl Powered</h2>
                <p>Every yera we organize the Girl Powered event at our local middle schools, with a turnout of around 30 to 50 aspiring young students</p>
                <ul style="list-style-position: inside; margin-top: 1rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
                    
                    <li>Introduced students to the design process and ran a fun bottle car activity to implement the process</li>
                    <li>Girls from South Brunswick middle schools were encouraged to create designs, make interpretations within their designs and build a plastic bottled car.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>